g.text: Embedded threads may swap between them,
But eventually one must call nce_halt_cpu()
This will stop that thread (and therefore
all other embedded SW threads in that CPU)
and transfer control back to the main thread
This is how Zephyr native_sim boots.
Variants of this boot are possible
